_:N4905339ec16744c99dac3132a977ce75 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Government Recruitment Service (<abbr title=\"Government Recruitment Service\">GRS</abbr>) was launched in September 2017 and is part of the Cabinet Office’s <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-people-group\">Government People Group</a>. </p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Government Recruitment Service\">GRS</abbr> provides operational delivery as well as specialist expertise, shares best practice and looks for new, innovative solutions to improve the recruitment process and experience.</p>\n\n<p>The service aspires to become the recruitment partner of choice for all Government departments, agencies and non-departmental public bodies. Technology, value for money, customer experience and the needs of a changing Civil Service are the pillars on which we continue to build and create.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Government Recruitment Service\">GRS</abbr> is run by civil servants for civil servants, with an in-depth understanding of how government works. We support recruitment for all roles and grades, including Senior Civil Servants, and have privileged access to and a deep understanding of the recruitment experience, best practice and compliance with Civil Service codes and regulations.</p>\n\n<p>Our service offer is built around customer needs, with the flexibility to take on as much or as little of a recruitment campaign as you need. We offer a personal service, which includes a dedicated account manager, and are able to supply robust data to recruiting departments.</p>\n\n<p>As a service, we have a commitment to continuous improvement to make sure that our customers are offered the latest in recruitment and candidates get the best experience. </p>\n\n<p>Our experienced Occupational Psychology team offers the latest in assessment and selection techniques, which includes accessible and research-driven online tests to support the selection of suitable candidates at the sift stage.</p>\n\n<p>We are also at the forefront of digital developments, supporting the transformation and implementation of a new <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.civilservicejobs.service.gov.uk/csr/index.cgi\">Civil Service Jobs site</a> to ensure hiring managers and applicants have a consistent, streamlined and positive experience.</p>\n\n<p>Our other dedicated teams also include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Recruiters and recruitment managers with experience in a variety of markets and sectors.</li>\n  <li>A broad range of operational delivery professionals, programme implementation experts, digital design and insight specialists.</li>\n  <li>Corporate services professionals, covering everything from Freedom of Information requests to communications</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Government Recruitment Service\">GRS</abbr> has recently been shortlisted for a string of recruitment awards, including: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>In-house Recruitment Awards 2023 finalist in the category of Recruitment Marketing Campaign. </li>\n  <li>Recruitment Marketing Awards 2023 finalist in the category of Recruitment Effectiveness. </li>\n  <li>Association of Business Psychology Award 2023, alongside partner Talogy, for Excellence in Digital Technology and highly commended for Bespoke/Customised Assessment </li>\n  <li>Recruitment Industry Disability Initiative (RIDI) award in the category of Inclusive Technology.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Find out more about our services in our brochures:</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690b1d1e7a88fd270a95fdc5/Government_Recruitment_Service_Brochure.pdf\">Government Recruitment Service Brochure</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.29 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">19 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67af0c7be270ceae39f9e1cf/In-House_Direct_Sourcing_Team_Brochure.pdf\">In-House Direct Sourcing Team Brochure</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">2.97 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">14 pages</span>)</span></p>\n\n<p>Or feel free to contact us at <a href=\"mailto:newbusiness.grs@cabinetoffice.gov.uk\">newbusiness.grs@cabinetoffice.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>" .
